name: EyeshadowLook
0:
”Alexa, ask eye shadow look picker”
”get eyeshadow help”
”what should I wear today”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: eyeshadow look picker
des: Deciding on what eye shadow to wear is very hard specially there's many to choose from. The skill will help you in choosing an eye shadow look. It includes variety of eye shadow look from natural to smoky looks. You can start the app by saying 'Open Eye Shadow Look Picker' or if you want more information, say 'help.' To get suggestion, say 'get eye shadow help' or 'give me makeup look.'
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
